Package quickSort

Class quickSortAnalysis

java.lang.Object
quickSort.quickSortAnalysis
public class quickSortAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
This class is a test program. A quickSort algorithm with recursion limit. The recursion limit varies from 2 to 300 by 2 steps, the array sized 20000 to 20480000. The result will be imported to Excel using Apache POI.
